Debian initscript for unicorn_rails.

 1. Save the files under the same structure of this repository:
    - /etc/init.d/unicorn_rails
    - /etc/default/unicorn_rails

 2. Configure the default settings files:
    - /etc/default/unicorn_rails

 3. Configure your projects settings files:
    - /etc/unicorn_rails.d/PROJ1.conf
    - /etc/unicorn_rails.d/PROJ2.conf

 4. Manage the daemons:
    - /etc/init.d/unicorn_rails start [ PROJ1 [ PROJ2 [ ... ] ] ]
    - /etc/init.d/unicorn_rails stop [ PROJ1 [ PROJ2 [ ... ] ] ]
    - /etc/init.d/unicorn_rails restart [ PROJ1 [ PROJ2 [ ... ] ] ]
